if RViz2 shows nothing / grey screen:

Make sure Terminal 1 (publisher node) is running first before opening RViz2
Check Fixed Frame is set to map

If we encounter an error saying ros2 command not found, type the following command in the terminal:
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash

In case we observe warning about byte values in PointCloud2:
This is a harmless ROS 2 Humble internal warning and does not affect the simulation
